<div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 p-5 text-sm text-amber-900 dark:border-amber-400/30 dark:bg-amber-500/10 dark:text-amber-100">
  <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Validation Troubleshooting</h2>
  <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
    <li><span class="font-medium">rejected credentials</span>: verify auth username/token for the provider account.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">request timed out</span>: verify network egress, firewall, DNS, and endpoint reachability from the Runway host.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">TLS validation failed</span>: paste a CA bundle (PEM) trusted for the endpoint certificate chain.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">redirected (HTTP 30x)</span>: endpoint is redirecting (often to login or different host); verify URL/protocol and provider selection.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">GitHub/Bitbucket on GitLab-backed endpoint</span>: Runway will also try GitLab API validation (`/api/v4/user`) with token auth when provider endpoints do not match.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">path not found (404)</span>: verify provider selection and endpoint URL.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">server error (5xx)</span>: check provider status and retry.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
